sentences: Kai Hahto (born 31 December 1973 in Vaasa, Finland) is a Finnish musician and drummer.
Hahto then recorded with the band Wintersun as a session drummer before joining them as a band member.

On 6 August 2014, it was announced that Hahto will be playing drums on the forthcoming Nightwish album, replacing Jukka Nevalainen, who went on hiatus from the band due to insomnia, and Hahto performed on all live shows since that date.

On July 15, 2019, Hahto became Nightwish's permanent drummer following Nevalainen's decision not to return to the band.
